Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw jerked her head up. Her eyes pierced through the dark to see a 
bot coming towards her. She growled at him, and took a step back into the 
dark.

"Stay away from me," she snarled harshly at Sniper. "You come any closer 
Maximal, and I will kill you!" The fool had mistaken her for Dinobot. If he 
chooses to come any closer, slag his hide, he will see his mistake.
